name: authenticate
description: authenticate to user account in clickup

name: setTimezone
description: set user timezone in IANA format based on which country or city user lives

name: getBalance
description: get user balance, usage and credit info

name: setJob
description: sets a task to search tasks in some clickup lists and find the report the ones with described details to user. user must mention the list ids they want to get report from

runType.description: define it's a one time instant job or it's a interval

schedule.description: schedule for the job in cronjob format. only of runType is interval

handler.description: the type of definition for this job

definition.description: definition of task with all details user mentioned.
